    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable mode of transportation, though it does show signs of age and regular use. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and occasional hesitation during gear changes that will eventually need attention. The exterior has several visible scratches and a small dent on the rear fender, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Recent maintenance includes a new battery and brake pads, but the tires are nearing the end of their lifespan and will likely need replacement within the next few months.",
